channel.title: Akyut - Apex
channel.description:
Bam! Another release, the second to last in my album. Took a lot of inspiration from @Phluze and @aUstin_Haga this time around, go and show them some love!
https://soundcloud.com/akyut/06-apex
The support I've gotten so far has been incredible, so thank you all for taking the time to listen and comment on my music. It means a lot!
Until next time.
